OL,5, Donald Campbell's restored Bluebird    
OL,6, will finally return to the Lake        
OL,7, District on Saturday, nearly 60 years  
OL,8, after the crash that claimed the       
OL,9, record-breaker's life. It follows a    
OL,10, painful saga that erupted into anger   
OL,11, and bitterness.                        
OL,13,FThe phone call, Gina Campbell          
OL,14,Frecollects, came "out of the blue".    
OL,16,FIntroducing himself as an amateur      
OL,17,Fdiver, Bill Smith outlined his ambition
OL,18,Fto locate Bluebird's crumpled wreckage 
OL,19,Fon the dark, unforgiving bed of        
OL,20,FConiston Water in England's North West.
